# Tidara Towers page

## Goal
Build a dedicated cinematic project page for **Tidara Towers** (أبراج تيدارا).

## Assets (do not read binary files — use paths only)
- Folder: `public/assets/projects/Tidara-tower/`
- Key files: `Hero.png`, `3D-Tower.png`, `Masterplan.png`, `Elevation:Facade.png`, `Interior 1.png`, `Interior 2.png`, `Walkthrough 1-3.png`, `Cinematic_architectural_film_.mp4`
- PDF plans: `public/assets/projects/Elshubaily Tidara Towers - Draft Plans - Cube -  ( 01-04-2026).pdf`

## Routing
- Generic placeholder: `src/routes/projects.$slug.tsx`
- Prefer dedicated route e.g. `src/routes/projects.tidara-towers.tsx` or `/projects/tidara-towers` if full custom layout is needed
- Match existing TanStack Start + Tailwind v4 patterns from homepage components

## Stack conventions
- Arabic RTL default; use `useLang()` from `@/contexts/lang-context`
- Reuse stone/plain surface classes from `src/styles.css` (`bg-plain-cream`, `bg-cover-slider-stone`, etc.)
- Asset path helper pattern: see `src/data/asset-paths.ts`
- Do not commit `.vercel/output`

## Performance
- Keep changes scoped to Tidara page + its components
- Avoid loading/indexing asset binaries; reference URLs like `/assets/projects/Tidara-tower/Hero.png`
